T02TD3519E:165a-5: lha mo tsunde lhag par che //
T02TD3519E:165a-6: yang dag rgyal ba de btud nas ;
T02TD3519E:165a-7: / dngos grub myur du rab 'grub pa //
T02TD3519E:165a-8: de yi sgrub thabs mdor bsdus brjod //
T02TD3519E:165a-9: dang por ri zhig sngags pas rang gi snying gar zla ba'i dbus su sa bon sde tshan gsum pa'i dang po la dang po'i lnga pas brgyan pas /
T02TD3519E:165a-10: zla phyed dang thig les spras pa ston ka'i zla ba'i 'od zer gyi phreng ba can /
T02TD3519E:165a-11: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis byin gyi rlabs kyis mdzes pa /
T02TD3519E:165a-12: de'i 'od zer las skyes pa'i bcom ldan 'das ma dang /
T02TD3519E:165a-13: bla ma dang sangs rgyas la sogs pa rnams bltas nas /
T02TD3519E:165a-14: mngon par phyag byas te sngags kyis mchod par bya'o //
T02TD3519E:165a-19: aom badzra nee bi dye h'um /
T02TD3519E:165a-21: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
T02TD3519E:165a-22: sdig pa thams cad so sor bshags //
T02TD3519E:165a-23: 'gro ba'i dge la rjes yi rang //
T02TD3519E:165a-24: sangs rgyas byang chub yid kyis gzung //
T02TD3519E:165a-26: de nas smon lam sngon du 'gro bas /
T02TD3519E:165a-27: sngags 'dis chos thams cad stong pa nyid bdag med par bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3519E:165a-28: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bhy'a ba a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD3519E:165a-29: de nas khams gsum pa ma lus pa sa bon sgyu ma'i rnam par bsams te /
T02TD3519E:165a-30: aom sva bh'a ba shuddha:sarba dharm'a:sva bh'a ba shuddho& ham /
T02TD3519E:165a-31: de nas sngon du gsungs pa'i sa bon las skyes pa'i dpal gyi lha mo tsunda'i bdag nyid du bsgom par bya ste /
T02TD3519E:165a-32: ston ka'i zla ba lta bu phyag bzhi pa /
T02TD3519E:165a-34: g-yon ba pustis mtshan pa'i padma bsnams pa /
T02TD3519E:165a-35: phyag gnyis kyis lhung bzed bsnams shing /
T02TD3519E:165a-36: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3519E:165a-37: padma dang zla ba la gnas pa bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3519E:165a-38: phyi nas phyag rgya bcing par bya ste /
T02TD3519E:165a-42: spyi bo rnams su srung ba byas nas bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD3519E:165a-43: de la phyag rgya ni 'di yin te /
T02TD3519E:165a-44: lag pa gnyis thal mo sbyar nas sdigs mdzub gnyis gung mo'i dkyil du 'khyil pa'i rnam par sbyar zhing mtheb chen gnyis logs su sbyar bar bya ste /
T02TD3519E:165b-2: aom tsa le tsu le tsunde sv'ah'a /
